331
00:24:54,744 --> 00:24:55,425
Your Majesty.

332
00:24:55,945 --> 00:24:58,425
I think what Official Mu said
is very true.

333
00:24:59,225 --> 00:25:00,544
The Protected Appointments System

334
00:25:00,985 --> 00:25:02,584
