Have you forgotten
how you were set on taking revenge

392
00:28:10,465 --> 00:28:12,425
and fighting to the death with Roujia?

393
00:28:13,504 --> 00:28:14,425
My Lord, I...

394
00:28:14,744 --> 00:28:16,784
I was just...

395
00:28:17,344 --> 00:28:18,304
