thinking of Mr. Sun.

588
00:37:13,460 --> 00:37:14,420
Sun Yunqian?

589
00:37:14,780 --> 00:37:15,500
Yes.

590
00:37:19,180 --> 00:37:22,900
He is indeed different
from other noble scholars.

591
00:37:24,180 --> 00:37:25,860
He has no arrogant
and peremptory manner.

592
