00:38:42,860 --> 00:38:43,780
Who am I?

612
00:38:44,580 --> 00:38:45,820
I am your father.

613
00:38:46,300 --> 00:38:48,900
You are the eldest son
of the Sun family.

614
00:38:49,780 --> 00:38:51,020
